description: Non-material amendment (repositioning of town houses) to planning permission P/2007/1071 dated 19/05/2008 for 'Demolition of buildings and construction of two three-storey terraces comprising 14 three-bedroom and 18 four-bedroom houses and part 4/5/6/7 storey building containing 249 flats (23 studios, 108 one-bedroom, 91 two-bedroom and 27 three-bedroom units) incorporating 63 key worker units; construction of two-storey refuse and energy centre building; provision of 271 car parking spaces, 320 cycle parking spaces; refuse storage in basement; landscaping and formation of emergency vehicle access road to Bromyard Avenue'
